Lucillo

Lucillo (Spanish pronunciation: [luˈθiʎo]) is a municipality located in the province of León, Castile and León, Spain.

Lucena de Jalón

Lucena de Jalón is a municipality located in the province of Zaragoza, Aragon, Spain.

Losacio

Losacio is a municipality located in the province of Zamora, Castile and León, Spain.

Los Villares de Soria

Los Villares de Soria is a municipality located in the province of Soria, Castile and León, Spain.

Los Llanos de Tormes

Los Llanos de Tormes is a municipality located in the province of Ávila, Castile and León, Spain.

Los Hinojosos

Los Hinojosos is a municipality in located in the province of Cuenca, Castile-La Mancha, Spain.

Los Cancajos

Los Cancajos is a large tourist resort in the Canarian island of La Palma. Its resident population is 713 (2013).

Los Barrios de Bureba

Los Barrios de Bureba is a municipality located in the province of Burgos, Castile and León, Spain.

Los Balbases

Los Balbases is a municipality located in the province of Burgos, Castile and León, Spain.

Loranca de Tajuña

Loranca de Tajuña is a municipality located in the province of Guadalajara, Castile-La Mancha, Spain.

Lora de Estepa

Lora de Estepa is a city located in the province of Seville, Spain.

Lomes

Lomes is a parish (administrative division) in Allande, a municipality within the province and autonomous community of Asturias, in northern Spain.

Loma de Ucieza

Loma de Ucieza is a municipality located in the province of Palencia, Castile and León, Spain.

Llucmajor (Barcelona Metro)

Llucmajor is a Barcelona Metro station, on L4. Part of the extension of that line from Guinardó into Nou Barris opened in 1982, it takes its name from Plaça de Llucmajor, the central square of the district.

Llofriu

Llanos de Olivenza

Llanos de Olivenza is a comarca in the province of Badajoz in the autonomous community of Extremadura, western Spain.

Llano de Bureba

Llano de Bureba is a municipality and town located in the province of Burgos, Castile and León, Spain.

Llamero, Asturias

Llamero is one of eleven parishes (administrative divisions) in Candamo, a municipality within the province and autonomous community of Asturias, in northern Spain.

Llamas, Asturias

Llamas (Asturian and official name: Ḷḷamas) is one of 18 parishes (administrative divisions) in Aller, a municipality within the province and autonomous community of Asturias, in northern Spain.

Llamas de la Ribera

Llamas de la Ribera (Spanish pronunciation: [ˈʎamaz ðe la riˈβeɾa]) is a municipality located in the province of León, Castile and León, Spain.

Lizartza

Lizartza is a town located in the province of Gipuzkoa, in the autonomous community of Basque Country, in the North of Spain.

Linares del Acebo

Linares del Acebo is one of 54 parish councils in Cangas del Narcea, a municipality within the province and autonomous community of Asturias, in northern Spain.
